,
HAVING REGARD TO REGULATION NO 31 ( EEC ) , 11 ( EAEC ) ( 1 ) ON THE STAFF REGULATIONS OF OFFICIALS AND THE CONDITIONS OF EMPLOYMENT OF OTHER SERVANTS OF THE EUROPEAN ECONOMIC COMMUNITY AND THE EUROPEAN ATOMIC ENERGY COMMUNITY , AND , IN PARTICULAR ARTICLE 14B OF ANNEX VII TO THOSE STAFF REGULATIONS AND ARTICLES 22 AND 67 OF THOSE CONDITIONS OF EMPLOYMENT ;
HAVING REGARD TO THE PROPOSALS FROM THE COMMISSION OF THE EUROPEAN ATOMIC ENERGY COMMUNITY AND THE COMMISSION OF THE EUROPEAN ECONOMIC COMMUNITY ;
WHEREAS IT IS FOR THE COUNCILS , ACTING IN ACCORDANCE WITH THE PROCEDURE REFERRED TO IN ARTICLE 65 ( 3 ) OF THE STAFF REGULATIONS , TO LAY DOWN THE LIST OF PLACES FOR WHICH A TRANSPORT ALLOWANCE MAY BE GRANTED , THE MAXIMUM AMOUNT OF THAT ALLOWANCE AND THE RULES FOR GRANTING IT ;
